    "We now focus our attention on the results obtained for the degree of data availability corresponding to ϵ = 0.001 as illustrated in Fig. 3b.",
    "We again observe that all the models are generalizing to unseen configurations with a lower cost than the minimum cost seen in the training data.",
    "For the first track, T1, we highlight that the QCBM provides the lowest utility compared to the other models while maintaining a competitive minimum value and diversity of high-quality solutions.",
    "For the second track, T2, we observe that the QCBM is competitive with the VAE while providing the best quality coverage C q.",
    "This point is clearer when analyzing and comparing the best quality-based metrics values in Fig. 4b."
